         <mark class="markperson"><span data-toggle="tooltip" title="Вера Ростова" class="person"><span class="sem_role" type="object"><span class="popuptext">object</span>Вера</span></span></mark> злая, бог с 
         <mark class="markperson"><span data-toggle="tooltip" title=" " class="person">ней</span></mark>! А все будет хорошо, и 
         <mark class="markperson"><span data-toggle="tooltip" title=" " class="person"><span class="sem_role" type="addressee"><span class="popuptext">addressee</span>маменьке</span></span></mark> 
         <mark class="markperson"><span data-toggle="tooltip" title=" " class="person">
               <mark class="markperson"><span data-toggle="tooltip" title="Наталья Ростова" class="person"><span class="sem_role" type="agent"><span class="popuptext">agent</span>она</span></span></mark></span></mark> не скажет; 
